data.description: Immaculate and practically brand-new! This meticulously maintained home sits on a fantastic lot, offering privacy with no direct neighbors to the rear. The well-designed floor plan includes a versatile downstairs bedroom perfect for use as an office, guest quarters, den, or playroom.  The spacious master suite boasts soaring ceilings and abundant natural light streaming in from the backyard. The kitchen is a social hub with a stunning design, featuring stainless appliances. Step into the backyard oasis, which opens up to green space adorned with citrus trees, creating a serene atmosphere.  Enjoy community amenities such as a pool and park. This home presents exceptional value for buyers seeking the polished feel of a new build. Don't miss the opportunity to own a residence that combines practicality with the allure of modern living.
